### chat api
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### signup user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "fullname": "jack2",
    "email": "jack2@122.com",
    "password": "123456",
    "workspace": "jack"
}

### signin user
# @name signin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "jack@122.com",
    "password": "123456",
    "ws_id": 1
}

@token = {{signin.response.body.token}}


### get users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### create chat
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chats
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "chat",
    "members": [1, 2, 3],
    "ws_id": 1,
    "public": true
}

### update chat
PATCH  http://localhost:8080/api/chats/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "chat",
    "members": [1, 2, 3],
    "ws_id": 1,
    "public": false
}

### get chat by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chats/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### delete chat
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/chats/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
